history.proof: intros x y H. sauto q: on depth: 3.

tactic: induction H as [a b Hab|a b c H1 H2 IH].
exceptions.exn: Expects a disjunctive pattern with 1 branch or a conjunctive pattern made of 3 patterns.

original: intros x y H. induction H as [a b Hab|a b c H1 H2 IH]. - apply star1. apply Hab. - eapply star_trans. + apply IH. + apply H2.
